Peter Lin, a Montebello, Calif.,physician, told the Securities and Exchange Commission he hasacquired 285,000 shares of Sierra Health Services Inc, or 5.1pct of the total outstanding common stock.    Lin said he bought the stock for about 1.7 mln dlrs solelyfor investment purposes.    Although he said he may buy more stock in Sierra HealthServices, Lin said he has no intention of seeking control ofthe company. Reuter&#3;